{"tid":726034,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃雨下行馬鞍山遭雷劈　18歲青年昏迷","createTime":"2018-07-02T05:42:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-02T13:10:35.000Z","uid":130626,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"b3abcd6b5962bb9ed6ab9c3cfd4643dfb3a7bbb5","tid":726034,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T05:42:10.000Z","msg":"馬鞍山有行山客被雷劈中。現場為馬鞍山麥理浩徑近昂平，今(2日)午12時許，黃色暴雨警告生效期間，一名18歲青年偕6友人在上址行山時，期間事主遭雷電擊中，當場昏迷，同行女友人立即報警。消防接報後登山搜救，政府飛行服務隊亦派直升機出動協助搜索，將其送往東區醫院搶救。 <br />\n<br />\n根據網上資料，昂平為位於高地的平原，面向西貢海峽，景色優美，乃露營熱點，同時亦是玩滑翔傘的勝地，有行山人士指該處山徑屬易行。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180702/mobile/bkn-20180702130120946-0702_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180702%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180702130120946-0702_00822_001.html&d=uLK1R3VyKD4%2BN24X34HBUtibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=6118d417\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180702/mobile/bkn-20180702130120946-0702_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"06a5ffafda1c9a16acfd998908c23ab1119ddb26","tid":726034,"uid":33875,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T05:44:36.000Z","msg":"好似唔係閃咗好多下，咁都中招唔好彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e55a29755132098acab27dc85a21fdbb335576e8","tid":726034,"uid":68215,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T05:45:28.000Z","msg":"落大雨重行山"},{"pid":"01db5b2d9d190995ac84bba99bde8b8699ac3e0a","tid":726034,"uid":66686,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"e55a29755132098acab27dc85a21fdbb335576e8","tid":726034,"uid":68215,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T05:45:28.000Z","msg":"落大雨重行山"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T05:47:04.000Z","msg":"打卡嘅野"},{"pid":"09a621d9640219323a25d81cb720579a7e4c53c9","tid":726034,"uid":14103,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"01db5b2d9d190995ac84bba99bde8b8699ac3e0a","tid":726034,"uid":66686,"li